creator: JOHELFY
descriptionHtml:
The Crocs en Scène company presents:

A professional space:
* The Actor's School (2-year professional school)
* A relay for professional actors in their search for network and contact.

An amateur area:
* Singing, theatrical interpretation and dance lessons.
* Annual show programming (plays, musicals, etc.)
* "Scènes pour Tous", the collective of theater companies from Grand Reims

An app to follow your desires and find your artistic path.
descriptionShort: Professional acting school and Drama company (courses and workshops)
